===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|boton|lang=fro}} (French {{term|bouton|lang=fr}}), itself either from {{etyl|LL.|en}} {{term/t|la|*bottōnem}}, probably ultimately from a {{etyl|gem|en}} language, or from {{term|bouter|lang=fr}} + {{term|-on|lang=fr}}.

